trans-unit.source: Indicates whether a control designer requires a preview instance of the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Indica se um estruturador do controlo requer uma instância de pré-visualização do controlo no momento da concepção.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: Apply the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute attribute to a control designer class to indicate the type of preview control that is supported by the control designer.
trans-unit.target: Aplique o atributo de SupportsPreviewControlAttribute a uma classe de estruturador do controlo para indicar o tipo de controlo de pré-visualização que é suportado pelo estruturador do controlo.

trans-unit.source: Use this attribute to change a preview control for design-time rendering without affecting the actual persisted instance of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Utilize este atributo para alterar um controlo de pré-visualização para composição de momento da conceção sem afetar a instância persistente real do controlo associado.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you specify the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute when declaring a custom designer class that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, especifique o SupportsPreviewControlAttribute quando declarar uma classe de designer personalizada que é derivada da <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>classe.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> property for the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute attribute determines the behavior for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> members in the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: O valor da <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>propriedade para o atributo SupportsPreviewControlAttribute determina o comportamento das <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>os membros de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>classe</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> base</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> property to `true` to indicate that the designer uses a temporary copy of the associated control to generate the design-time HTML.
trans-unit.target: Definir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>propriedade `true` para indicar que o estruturador utiliza uma cópia temporária do controlo associado para gerar o HTML momento da concepção.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes to the temporary control are not persisted.
trans-unit.target: As alterações para o controlo temporário não são mantidas.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> property to `false` to indicate that the designer returns the control instance, specifically the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A> property, from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Definir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>propriedade `false` para indicar que o estruturador devolve a instância de controlo, especificamente o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A>propriedade, do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes to the control object are persisted.
trans-unit.target: Alterações ao objeto de controlo são mantidas.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CalendarDesigner> class is marked with the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CalendarDesigner>classe estiver marcada com SupportsPreviewControlAttribute definido como `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CalendarDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The designer uses the preview control with the automatic style formatting task, which allows the user to preview various autoformat stylesthat can be applied to the calendar.
trans-unit.target: O estruturador utiliza o controlo de pré-visualização com o estilo automático tarefas de formatação, que permite ao utilizador pré-visualizar vários autoformat stylesthat podem ser aplicadas ao calendário.

trans-unit.source: As the user selects different autoformat styles in the user interface, the selected style scheme is applied to the preview control.
trans-unit.target: Como o utilizador seleciona autoformat diferentes estilos na interface de utilizador, o esquema de estilo selecionado é aplicado ao controlo de pré-visualização.

trans-unit.source: Applying a new style to the preview control does not change the scheme that is applied to the instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar> control in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Aplicar um novo estilo para o controlo de pré-visualização não altera o esquema que seja aplicado à instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar>controlo no designer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Calendar>

trans-unit.source: If the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute is not specified in the control designer declaration, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> behavior is equivalent to specifying the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> as `false`.
trans-unit.target: Se o SupportsPreviewControlAttribute não for especificado na declaração estruturador do controlo, o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>comportamento é equivalente a especificar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A>como `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.SupportsPreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Designer classes derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> members, and ignore the SupportsPreviewControlAttribute attribute.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Designer classes derivam o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>classe pode substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>Membros e ignorar o atributo SupportsPreviewControlAttribute.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: To determine the expected behavior for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>, see the reference documentation for the derived control designer class.
trans-unit.target: Para determinar o comportamento esperado para <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>, consulte a documentação de referência para a classe de designer derivada do controlo.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: For general information about using attributes, see [Attributes Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a4daf212-2410-423d-a800-7a08864e9bff) and [Attributes](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter informações gerais sobre a utilização de atributos, consulte [descrição geral de atributos](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a4daf212-2410-423d-a800-7a08864e9bff) e [atributos](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre o momento da conceção atributos, consulte [atributos e suporte do momento da conceção](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the control designer requires a temporary preview control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o estruturador do controlo requer um controlo de pré-visualização temporário no momento da concepção.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you specify a value for the SupportsPreviewControl property by applying the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> attribute to a custom designer class declaration.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, especifique um valor para a propriedade SupportsPreviewControl aplicando o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>atributo para uma declaração de classe de designer personalizada.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The value of the SupportsPreviewControl property for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> attribute determines the behavior for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> members in the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: O valor da propriedade SupportsPreviewControl para o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>atributo determina o comportamento das <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>os membros de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>classe</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> base</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Set the SupportsPreviewControl property to `true` to indicate that the designer uses a temporary copy of the associated control to generate the design-time HTML.
trans-unit.target: Defina a propriedade SupportsPreviewControl como `true` para indicar que o estruturador utiliza uma cópia temporária do controlo associado para gerar o momento da conceção HTML.

trans-unit.source: Changes to the temporary control are not persisted.
trans-unit.target: As alterações para o controlo temporário não são mantidas.

trans-unit.source: Set the SupportsPreviewControl property to `false` to indicate that the designer returns the control instance, specifically the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A> property, from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Defina a propriedade SupportsPreviewControl como `false` para indicar que o estruturador devolve a instância de controlo, especificamente o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A>propriedade, do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Component%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes to the control object are persisted.
trans-unit.target: Alterações ao objeto de controlo são mantidas.
